data.description: Welcome home! Looking for a charming main floor living style home in Tonganoxie, KS? Look no further! Step inside to a cozy living room with an inviting electric fireplace, perfect for winter evenings with vaulted ceilings. The eat-in kitchen features stainless steel appliances (that stay!), NEW sink, and hardware, ready to start cooking! Primary bedroom has a walk-in closet and a skylight in the full bathroom. This move-in-ready home boasts recent upgrades like a NEW front porch, back patio, ceiling fans, light fixtures, and an epoxy-coated garage floor. The roof was also replaced in 2021. With a 2-car garage and backyard shed, you'll have ample storage space. Don't miss out on this opportunity—schedule a viewing today before it's gone!
